{"tid":97260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成田機場免費500M網卡　台港旅客優先用","createTime":"2017-01-27T13:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T04:04:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f217648b26dcc3e56cf55b3f539ed9892d509c","tid":97260,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"2017年01月27日17:50 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170127/640_61f43cbca309318b74f7420c250f1b6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170127%2F640_61f43cbca309318b74f7420c250f1b6f.jpg&h=3b687532&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n翻攝YAHOO JAPAN <br />\n<br />\n訪日觀光客有免費網路可用了！日本成田機場昨天宣佈，自下月2月1日起機場內免費發放SIM卡，一開始會提供給香港與台灣旅客（繁體字版本），之後陸續會有簡體字、英文、韓文。使用免費SIM卡旅客必須先登錄「WAmazing」，使用期間為5日，可免費使用網路傳輸量為500M，可以付費追加。 <br />\n<br />\n（余浚安／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170127/1045102/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170127%2F1045102%2F1%2F&d=za12ywSivCnp80l6%2BeUfg0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=dd3941a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170127/1045102/1/</a>"},{"pid":"63d25045bb4e68892166fb19b9370095ff9b230c","tid":97260,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afb77fd01dc387d405d18e2aafe3093c25616a7","tid":97260,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b9c30feeaf45be5865781c03023d8b02931d4f","tid":97260,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.